cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on transferring visuo-motor policies to real-world robotic tasks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a modular deep reinforcement learning method. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper discusses a visually-guided robot reaching task and achieving pixel accuracy. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning method for transferring models from simulation to real-world tasks. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the bottleneck between perception and control in the proposed method.
